item.title: CVE-2023-2324|2023-07-05T10:47:56.883Z -- unknown -- elementor%20forms%20google%20sheet%20connector
item.description: The Elementor Forms Google Sheet Connector WordPress plugin before 1.0.7, gsheetconnector-for-elementor-forms-pro WordPress plugin through 1.0.7 does not escape some parameters before outputting them back in attributes, leading to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high privilege users such as admin
